      <span class="living comments_link"><a href="http://www.alternet.org/comments/drugs/denied-liver-transplant-using-medical-marijuana-and-dying-it-heartlessness-prohibition#disqus_thread" class="comments disqus-comments" data-disqus-identifier="node/830090">Comments</a></span>
